<h2 id="points-vectors-in-homogeneous-coordinates" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#points-vectors-in-homogeneous-coordinates"><span>Points &amp; Vectors in Homogeneous Coordinates</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>Homogeneous coordinates에서는,
<ul>
<li><strong>3D point</strong>: $ (x, y, z, \mathbf{1}) $</li>
<li><strong>3D vector</strong>: $ (x, y, z, \mathbf{0}) $</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>→ 이 표현은 coordinate-free geometric programming의 개념과 <strong>완전하게 일치하는 모델</strong>을 제공함</p>
