<h2 id="_2-affine-transformation-matrix-defines-an-affine-frame-w-r-t-world-frame" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-affine-transformation-matrix-defines-an-affine-frame-w-r-t-world-frame"><span>2) Affine Transformation Matrix Defines an Affine Frame w.r.t. World Frame</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>행렬 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="bold">M</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathbf{M}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6861em;"></span><span class="mord mathbf">M</span></span></span></span>은 <strong>기준 프레임 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">{</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\{0\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">{</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mclose">}</span></span></span></span> 기준으로 표현된 body frame <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">{</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\{1\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">{</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mclose">}</span></span></span></span>을 정의</strong></li>
<li><span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="bold">M</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathbf{M}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6861em;"></span><span class="mord mathbf">M</span></span></span></span>의 각 column은 다음을 나타냄:
<ul>
<li>앞의 3개 column: 축 벡터</li>
<li>마지막 column: 원점 위치</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>→ <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="bold">M</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathbf{M}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6861em;"></span><span class="mord mathbf">M</span></span></span></span>은 <strong>body frame <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">{</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\{1\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">{</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mclose">}</span></span></span></span>을 world frame <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">{</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\{0\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">{</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mclose">}</span></span></span></span> 기준으로 표현</strong>한 것</p>
<h2 id="examples" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#examples"><span>Examples</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>같은 물체의 body frame을 두 방식으로 정의:
<ol>
<li>world frame과 동일한 위치일 때</li>
<li>이동된 위치에서 정의될 때</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
<p>→ 두 경우 모두 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="bold">M</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathbf{M}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6861em;"></span><span class="mord mathbf">M</span></span></span></span>은 body frame을 world 기준으로 표현함</p>
<h2 id="_3-affine-transformation-matrix-transforms-a-point-in-body-frame-to-the-same-point-but-represented-in-world-frame" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-affine-transformation-matrix-transforms-a-point-in-body-frame-to-the-same-point-but-represented-in-world-frame"><span>3) Affine Transformation Matrix Transforms a Point in Body Frame to (the same) Point (but) represented in World Frame</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>$ \mathbf{p}^{\{1\}} = \begin{bmatrix}1 \ 1 \ 0\end{bmatrix} $<br>
(body frame <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mrow><mn>1</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\\{1\\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mspace newline"></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace newline"></span></span></span></span></span> 기준의 점)</li>
</ul>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="bold">p</mi><mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mrow><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace></mrow></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="bold">M</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="bold">p</mi><mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mrow><mn>1</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace></mrow></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathbf{p}^{\\{0\\}} = \mathbf{M} \cdot \mathbf{p}^{\\{1\\}}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0585em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">p</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8641em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mspace mtight newline"></span><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">0</span><span class="mspace mtight newline"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6861em;"></span><span class="mord mathbf">M</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">⋅</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0585em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">p</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8641em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mspace mtight newline"></span><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span><span class="mspace mtight newline"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li>같은 점을 <strong>world frame <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mrow><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\\{0\\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mspace newline"></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mspace newline"></span></span></span></span></span> 기준으로 표현한 것</strong><br>
Why?</li>
<li>동일한 물체를 body frame에서 보다가 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="bold">M</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathbf{M}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6861em;"></span><span class="mord mathbf">M</span></span></span></span>을 통해 <strong>world frame 기준 표현</strong>으로 변환한 것:</li>
</ul>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="bold">p</mi><mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mrow><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace></mrow></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="bold">M</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="bold">p</mi><mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mrow><mn>1</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace></mrow></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathbf{p}^{\\{0\\}} = \mathbf{M} \cdot \mathbf{p}^{\\{1\\}}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0585em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">p</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8641em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mspace mtight newline"></span><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">0</span><span class="mspace mtight newline"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6861em;"></span><span class="mord mathbf">M</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">⋅</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0585em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">p</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8641em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mspace mtight newline"></span><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span><span class="mspace mtight newline"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li>단순히 geometry를 변환한 이야기임</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="directions-of-the-arrow" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#directions-of-the-arrow"><span>Directions of the &quot;arrow&quot;</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>첫 번째 의미
<ul>
<li>geometry 자체를 transform (frame은 그대로)</li>
